title: Heaven 17 - Commodore User
description:
Three melodies by Heaven Seventeen, played by a Commodore 64.:
- Key to the World
- Crushed by the wheels of industry
- Temptation

It\&#039;s from a flexi disk that once graced the cover of Commodore User,as an ad for what you could do with a Commodore 64 and a \"The Music System\" From Rainbird Software. 

Quality is... so-so. It\&#039;s from a flexi disk... ;-)
